title: Sound On: Inflation, Biden Agenda Delay

description:
Guests: Betsey Stevenson, Professor of Economics and Public Policy at University of Michigan, former Member of the Council of Economic Advisers, Dan Katz, former Senior Advisor at the U.S. Treasury Department and co-founder of Amberwave Partners, and Bloomberg politics contributors, Rick Davis and Jeanne Sheehan Zaino.
